erlusb 0.5
  * Remove all code and tests not needed for the OTP application
  * Exclusively support libusb-1.0
  * Write Erlang code as OTP application
  * Improved debug logs with file name, line number, function name
  * Switch tarballs from lzma to xz compression
  * README now in rst format, and with more elaborate content.

erlusb 0.4
  * Rudimentary libusb-1.0 support.
  * Only generate dist tarballs with lzma compression.
  * Migrate Erlang/C interface to ei API
  * Add skeleton file with GPS device support
  * Use new git tags for releases: release/erlusb-0.4

erlusb 0.3
  * Update stuff to work in git managed source tree.

erlusb 0.2.3
  * Introduce beginning of autotest based testsuite.

erlusb 0.2.2
  * Introduce ERLCFLAGS and AM_ERLCFLAGS.
  * Use proper installation directories for erlusb library components.

erlusb 0.2.1
  * Use Erlang macros introduced in autoconf 2.60 or 2.61

erlusb 0.2.0
  * automake option subdir-objects
  * valgrind tests

erlusb 0.1.1
  * 'make distclean' clean.

erlusb 0.1.0
  * LGPL Licensing.
  * Proof-of-concept for passing libusb C data to Erlang.

erlusb 0.0.4
  * Beefed up second erlang testcase.

erlusb 0.0.3
  * Second erlang testcase.

erlusb 0.0.2
  * Reorganized directories.

erlusb 0.0.1
  * 'make distclean' clean.

erlusb 0.0.0
  * First tests.
